Line: - LRA1 (pinky-edge ulnar) — "incoming message" attention pulse, easy to feel through cuff thickness.

File: public\Projects\LibraryOfBabel\BLUEPRINT_REPOSITORY\chillblast-freezer\ARCHITECTURE.md:112
