File: public\Projects\LibraryOfBabel\BLUEPRINT_REPOSITORY\chillblast-freezer\ARCHITECTURE.md:118
Line: **MAX30205 skin-temp ×2** — medical-grade I²C digital thermometer, ±0.1 °C, two units: cuff inner (against radial artery) and back-of-hand. Frostbite alert threshold: skin temp at radial artery <15 °C for >5 min, OR back-of-hand <8 °C instantaneous. Both thresholds are configurable per worker via the supervisor console.

